      <title>冬季风暴敲开力量，马刺在肯塔基州洪水泛滥</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/winter-storm-knocks-out-power-spurs-floods-in-kentucky</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一场巨大的冬季风暴造成了毁灭性的洪水，至少造成了八人死亡，肯塔基州席卷了整个美国的数百个航班，并向南部有超过500万客户淘汰了电力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/winter-storm-knocks-out-power-spurs-floods-in-kentucky</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 14:45:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>恢复英国通货膨胀将保持削减税率的谨慎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-15/resurging-uk-inflation-will-keep-boe-cautious-on-cutting-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国通货膨胀率可能在一月份的10个月内达到了最高水平，持续的价格压力恢复了，这使得英格兰银行因急于削减利率而保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-15/resurging-uk-inflation-will-keep-boe-cautious-on-cutting-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Feb 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
